A Jack of all trades, King of none is a saying referring to one competent in many endeavors but excelling in none. One such example is the [[Charlatan]] in Age of Wonders. Wikipedia itself could be considered a "Jack of all trades, King of none" since it has information on all subjects, but doesn't have exceptional information on any.

The full expression is 'Jack of all trades, King of none, ofttimes better than King of one.', perhaps highlighting the advantage of adaptability over specialization, best demonstrated by our survival as a race.